arStrings.szText: Fayira will be in her father’s good hands by now. He was once a member of the Pale Hand, and understands my work with Lorath—this wouldn’t be the first time it pulled me from home. He will bring her here when it is safe.

Fay’s learned to smith blades, but not to work with their wielders. So, once I’m set up here, it will be time to begin the next stage of her training. I wish it was not so, but this is the world she is inheriting.
